{"id": 2982, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在手机里都发现了哪些“app 孤岛化”现象？", "description": "所谓的“互联网时代”走到今天，app 们似乎反而变成了一个个数据孤岛。（题图来自：iStock ©️ mustafahacalaki）", "record_count": 15786, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190828235203pdITxl7J54261g0t.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-08-31T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5874, "title": "你在手机里都发现了哪些“app 孤岛化”现象？", "content": "你在手机里都发现了哪些“信息孤岛化”现象？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 345908, "content": "淘宝里的商品链接无法直接分享到微信", "image": "img/option/option/20190829151226BxJ7jC8ZKPOuTwHA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345909, "content": "大部分搜索引擎都没办法直接搜索微信文章", "image": "img/option/option/20190829151113rGv7BqAV5uyphlXK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345910, "content": "微博里提到“公众号”“x红书”之类的词，可能会被限流", "image": "img/option/option/201908291512569PKRoAiDsS0B1LOq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345911, "content": "同一个链接，有时要用特定的浏览器/ app 才能打开", "image": "img/option/option/201908291012204GcYFzdaKBlV8bf2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345915, "content": "为了听歌/看视频，往往要买好几家音乐/视频网站会员", "image": "img/option/option/20190829150518Nxl5n6gsVhcaGOwC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345916, "content": "搜索引擎经常搜不到有用信息，只能去 app 里搜索 ", "image": "img/option/option/20190829100914uDT1VMHUZgPWR9Gm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345922, "content": "各种应用都可以被分成“某某系”（比如“腾讯系”“阿里系”）", "image": "img/option/option/20190829100141BOMwmeAioV7k0cS4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345925, "content": "比起装一堆同类应用，聚合类 app 有时反而更好使", "image": "img/option/option/20190828235632M9soxX3kLUgHDmBJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}